definition.value:
Unique code or number identifying the location measurement, should be UUID. Example: urn:uuid:2e82976a-35d6-4870-a4d5-d79abf772a8f

Example:
~~~
"identifier": [
     {
         "system":"urn:ietf:rfc:3986",
         "value":"urn:uuid:a76d9bbf-f293-4fb7-ad4c-2851cac77162"
     }
]
~~~

